title: (Tues Early Bird) Ashley McBryde Calls Us With Some Big Show News! + Bryan Swanson from 'Breaking Bobby Bones' Is On The Show Answering FAQs About Removing Animals + Mailbag: Listener's Boyfriend Still Has Ex-Wife's Clock...
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) Ashley McBryde Calls Us With Some Big Show News! + Bryan Swanson from 'Breaking Bobby Bones' Is On The Show Answering FAQs About Removing Animals + Mailbag: Listener's Boyfriend Still Has Ex-Wife's Clock...
description:
Ashley McBryde calls into the show to share some big news with the show about something we just won... Plus, Bryan Swanson who was on 'Breaking Bobby Bones' and owns a business removing animals from people's homes calls in to answer some facts for Bobby about removing the foxes from his yard. Mailbag: A listener writes in to tell us her boyfriend still has a clock up in his house that was from his ex-wife, and it has their wedding date on it... she wants to take it down but he doesn't. We give our best advice!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
